         <div type="colophon" xml:lang="tam-Latn">
          <head>Edition</head>
            <pb n="GL" facs="to-be-filled"/>
            <ab>
               <milestone unit="section" type="date"/>
               <date notBefore="1865-08-15"  notAfter="1869-10-23" type="ciclical"/>
               <seg type="date-y" subtype="v-mk"><lb type="prose" n="r6col3"/> piṟacoṟpatti <g facs="#yk1a">YJ1a</g>m</seg> – 
               <seg type="date-m" subtype="v-mk">māci <g  facs="#m">m°</g></seg>
               <seg type="date-md" subtype="v-mk" n="digit-c"> <lb type="prose" n="r7col3"/> 5 <supplied resp="#mafr"><g facs="#t"
                     >t°</g></supplied> </seg>  
               <seg type="borForm"  subtype="o">mēlteru  <persName ref="pers:to-be-filled" role="owner">tēṉāmuttayā<lb type="prose" n="r8col3"/>piḷḷai</persName>
                  <rs ref="pers:to-be-filled">vayittiliṅka paṇṭārattiṉiṭattil</rs> <lb type="prose" n="r9col3"/>  <seg type="title" subtype="v"><name type="title" ref="to-be-filled">vētāraṇiya<hi rend="grantha">stala</hi>purāṇam</name></seg>
                  eraval ā<lb type="prose" n="r10col3"/>y kuṭuttiruttatu – vāṅka vēṇṭiyatu </seg></ab>
         </div>
         <div type="translation">
            <head>Translation</head>
            <p>In the Jovian year Piṟacoṟpatti, month of Māci, 5th day, Tēṉāmuttayāpiḷḷai of Western
               street gave as a borrowing (<foreign xml:lang="tam-Latn">eraval</foreign>, colloquial for <foreign  xml:lang="tam-Latn">iraval</foreign>) the <foreign xml:lang="tam-Latn">Vētāraṇiyastalapurāṇam</foreign>
               to Vayittiliṅkapaṇṭāram. It should be collected.</p>
         </div>
